msgstr "通过定义 CAPI 资源创建下游群集"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:116
msgid ""
"This guide assumes an existing RKE2 cluster and Rancher (including cert-"
