"置文件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:137 l10n/source/edge.xml:3619
msgid ""
"<literal>downstream-cluster-config.yaml</literal> is the image definition "
"file, see <xref linkend=\"quickstart-eib\"/> for more details."
msgstr ""
"<literal>downstream-cluster-config.yaml</literal> "
"是映像定义文件，有关详细信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"quickstart-eib\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:138
msgid ""
"The base image when downloaded is <literal>xz</literal> compressed, which "
"must be uncompressed with <literal>unxz</literal> and copied/moved under the "
"<literal>base-images</literal> folder."
msgstr ""
"下载的基础映像已经过 <literal>xz</literal> 压缩，必须使用 <literal>unxz</"
"literal> 将其解压缩，并将其复制/移动到 <literal>base-images</literal> "
"文件夹中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:139
