msgstr ""
"然后通过 <literal>preprovisioningNetworkDataName</literal> 规范字段在 "
"<literal>BareMetalHost</literal> 资源中引用该机密。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:176
msgid ""
"In some circumstances the MAC address may be omitted. See <xref "
