#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:315
msgid "Boot the downstream nodes"
msgstr "引导下游节点"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:316
msgid ""
"Now that we have created the installation media, we can boot our downstream "
"nodes with it."
msgstr "现在我们已创建安装媒体，接下来可以用它来引导下游节点。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:317
msgid ""
"For each of the systems that you want to control with Elemental, add the "
"installation media and boot the device. After installation, it will reboot "
"and register itself."
msgstr "对于您要使用 Elemental "
"控制的每个系统，请添加安装媒体并引导设备。安装后，系统会重引导并自行注册。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:318
msgid ""
"If you are using the UI extension, you should see your node appear in the "
"\"Inventory of Machines.\""
msgstr "如果您正在使用 UI 扩展，则应会看到您的节点出现在“Inventory of Machines”（计算"
"机清单）中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:319
msgid ""
"Do not remove the installation medium until you’ve seen the login prompt; "
"during first-boot files are still accessed on the USB stick."
msgstr "在出现登录提示之前，请勿移除安装媒体；在首次引导期间，仍需访问 USB "
"记忆棒上的文件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:320
msgid "Create downstream clusters"
msgstr "创建下游群集"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:321
msgid ""
"There are two objects we need to create when provisioning a new cluster "
"using Elemental."
msgstr "使用 Elemental 置备新群集时，需要创建两个对象。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:322
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:323
msgid ""
"The first is the <literal>MachineInventorySelectorTemplate</literal>. This "
"object allows us to specify a mapping between clusters and the machines in "
"the inventory."
msgstr ""
"第一个对象是 "
"<literal>MachineInventorySelectorTemplate</literal>。此对象用于指定群集与清单"
"中计算机之间的映射。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:324
msgid ""
"Create a selector which will match any machine in the inventory with a label:"
msgstr "创建一个选择器，用于根据标签匹配清单中的任何计算机："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:325
msgid "Apply the resource to the cluster:"
msgstr "将资源应用于群集："

