#: l10n/source/edge.xml:392
msgid ""
"As a simple example to demonstrate this, we are going to install the "
"<literal>nvidia-container-toolkit</literal> RPM package found in the third "
"party vendor-supported NVIDIA repository:"
msgstr ""
"我们通过一个简单的示例来演示这一点：我们将安装由第三方供应商提供支持的 "
"NVIDIA 储存库中的 <literal>nvidia-container-toolkit</literal> RPM 软件包："

