"The built ISO image is stored at <literal>$CONFIG_DIR/eib-image.iso</"
"literal>:"
msgstr "构建的 ISO 映像存储在 <literal>$CONFIG_DIR/eib-image.iso</literal> 中："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:415
msgid ""
"Each build creates a time-stamped folder in <literal>$CONFIG_DIR/_build/</"
"literal> that includes the logs of the build, the artifacts used during the "
"build, and the <literal>combustion</literal> and <literal>artefacts</"
"literal> directories which contain all the scripts and artifacts that are "
"added to the CRB image."
msgstr ""
"每次构建时都会在 <literal>$CONFIG_DIR/_build/</literal> "
"中创建一个带时间戳的文件夹，其中包含构建日志、构建期间使用的制品以及 "
"<literal>combustion</literal> 和 <literal>artefacts</literal> 目录，"
"这两个目录包含添加到 CRB 映像的所有脚本和制品。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:416
msgid "The contents of this directory should look like:"
msgstr "此目录的内容如下所示："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:417
msgid ""
"If the build fails, <literal>eib-build.log</literal> is the first log that "
"contains information. From there, it will direct you to the component that "
"failed for debugging."
msgstr ""
"如果构建失败，首先会在 <literal>eib-build.log</literal> "
"中记录相关信息。该日志会指出哪个组件构建失败，方便您进行调试。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:418
msgid "At this point, you should have a ready-to-use image that will:"
msgstr "此时，您应该有了一个随时可用的映像，它可以："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:419
msgid "Deploy SUSE Linux Micro 6.1"
msgstr "部署 SUSE Linux Micro 6.1"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:420
msgid "Configure the root password"
msgstr "配置 root 口令"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:421
msgid "Install the <literal>nvidia-container-toolkit</literal> package"
msgstr "安装 <literal>nvidia-container-toolkit</literal> 软件包"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:422
msgid "Configure an embedded container registry to serve content locally"
msgstr "配置嵌入的容器仓库以在本地处理内容"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:423
msgid "Install single-node RKE2"
msgstr "安装单节点 RKE2"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:424
msgid "Configure static networking"
msgstr "配置静态网络"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:425
msgid "Install KubeVirt"
msgstr "安装 KubeVirt"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:426
msgid "Deploy a user-supplied manifest"
msgstr "部署用户提供的清单"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:427
msgid "Debugging the image build process"
msgstr "调试映像构建过程"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:428
msgid ""
"If the image build process fails, refer to the <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/release-1.3/docs/"
"debugging.md\">upstream debugging guide</link>."
msgstr ""
"如果映像构建过程失败，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/"
"edge-image-builder/blob/release-1.3/docs/debugging.md\">上游调试指南</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:429
msgid "Testing your newly built image"
msgstr "测试新构建的映像"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:430
msgid ""
"For instructions on how to test the newly built CRB image, refer to the "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/"
"release-1.3/docs/testing-guide.md\">upstream image testing guide</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关如何测试新构建的 CRB 映像的说明，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/release-1.3/docs/testing-guide."
"md\">上游映像测试指南</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:432
msgid ""
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager is included in SUSE Edge to provide automation and "
"control for keeping SUSE Linux Micro as the underlying operating system "
"consistently up-to-date on all nodes of your edge deployment. It can also be "
"used to manage Kubernetes and applications deployed on Kubernetes on your "
"edge nodes."
msgstr ""
"SUSE Edge 中包含的 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 可提供自动化管理功能，确保边缘部"
"署的所有节点上作为底层操作系统的 SUSE Linux Micro 始终保持最新状态。它还可用"
"于管理边缘节点上的 Kubernetes 以及在 Kubernetes 上部署的应用程序。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:433
msgid ""
"This quickstart guide is intended to get you up to speed with SUSE Multi-"
"Linux Manager as quickly as possible, with the goal of providing operating "
"system updates to your edge nodes. The quickstart guide doesn’t discuss "
"topics like sizing your storage, creating and managing additional software "
"channels for staging purposes, or managing users, system groups, and "
"organizations for larger deployments. For production use, we strongly "
"recommend to get familiar with the comprehensive <link xl:href=\"https://"
"documentation.suse.com/suma/5.0/en/suse-manager/index.html\">SUSE Multi-"
"Linux Manager Documentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"本快速入门指南旨在帮助您尽快熟悉 SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager，目标是为您的边缘节点提供操作系统更新。本快速入门指南不会涉及诸如调整"
"存储容量、创建和管理用于过渡的额外软件通道，或是针对大规模部署场景管理用户、"
"系统组及组织等主题。对于生产用途，我们强烈建议您熟悉内容全面的 <link xl:href="
"\"https://documentation.suse.com/suma/5.0/en/suse-manager/index.html\">SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager 文档</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:434
msgid ""
"The following steps are required to prepare SUSE Edge for using SUSE Multi-"
"Linux Manager effectively:"
msgstr "要使 SUSE Edge 能够有效使用 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager，需执行以下步骤："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:435
msgid "Deploy and configure SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server."
msgstr "部署并配置 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 服务器。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:436
msgid "Sync the SUSE Linux Micro package repositories."
msgstr "同步 SUSE Linux Micro 软件包储存库。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:437
msgid "Create system groups."
msgstr "创建系统组。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:438
msgid "Create activation keys."
msgstr "创建激活密钥。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:439
msgid ""
"Use Edge Image Builder to prepare installation media for SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager registration"
msgstr "使用 Edge Image Builder 准备用于 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 注册的安装媒体。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:440
msgid "Deploy SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server"
msgstr "部署 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 服务器"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:441
msgid ""
"If you already have an instance of SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 5.0.5 running, "
"you can skip this step."
msgstr "如果您已在运行 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 5.0.5 实例，则可跳过此步骤。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:442
msgid ""
"You can run SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server on a dedicated physical server, "
"as a virtual machine on your own hardware, or in the cloud. Pre-configured "
"virtual machine images for SUSE Multi-Linux Server are provided for "
"supported public clouds."
msgstr ""
"您可以在专用物理服务器、自有硬件上的虚拟机或云中运行 SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager 服务器。针对受支持的公有云，我们提供了预配置的 SUSE Multi-Linux "
"服务器虚拟机映像。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:443
msgid ""
"In this quick start we’re using the \"qcow2\" image <literal>SUSE-Manager-"
"Server.x86_64-5.0.4-Qcow-5.0-2025-04.qcow2</literal> for AMD64/Intel 64 that "
"you can find at <link xl:href=\"https://www.suse.com/download/suse-manager/"
"\">https://www.suse.com/download/suse-manager/</link> or in the SUSE "
"Customer Center. This image will work as a virtual machine on hypervisors "
"like KVM. Please always check for the newest version of the image and use it "
"for new installations."
msgstr ""
"在本快速入门中，我们针对 AMD64/Intel 64 体系结构使用“qcow2”映像 <literal"
">SUSE-Manager-Server.x86_64-5.0.4-Qcow-5.0-2025-04.qcow2</literal>，您可通过 "
"<link xl:href=\"https://www.suse.com/download/suse-manager/\">https://"
"www.suse.com/download/suse-manager/</link> 或 SUSE Customer Center 获取该映像"
"。此映像可在 KVM 等超级管理程序上作为虚拟机运行。请务必检查是否有可用的最新版"
"映像，并在执行全新安装时使用最新版本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:444
msgid ""
"You can also install SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server on any of the other "
"supported hardware architectures. In that case pick the image that matches "
"your hardware architecture."
msgstr ""
"您也可以在其他任何受支持的硬件体系结构上安装 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"服务器。在这种情况下，请选择与您的硬件体系结构相匹配的映像。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:445
msgid ""
"Once you have downloaded the image, create a virtual machine that meets at "
"least the following minimal hardware specifications:"
msgstr "下载映像后，请创建一台至少满足以下最低硬件规格的虚拟机："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:446
msgid "16 GB RAM"
msgstr "16 GB RAM"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:447
msgid "4 physical or virtual cores"
msgstr "4 个物理或虚拟核心"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:448
msgid "an additional block device that has at least 100 GB"
msgstr "一个至少 100 GB 的额外块设备"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:449
msgid ""
"With the qcow2 image, there is no need to install the operating system. You "
"can directly attach the image as your root partition."
msgstr "使用 qcow2 映像时，无需安装操作系统。您可以直接将该映像挂接为根分区。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:450
msgid ""
"You need to set up the network so that your edge nodes can later access SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager Server with a hostname that contains the fully qualified "
"domain name (\"FQDN\")!"
msgstr ""
"您需要设置网络，以便您的边缘节点日后能够通过包含完全限定域名（简称“FQDN”）"
"的主机名访问 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 服务器！"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:451
msgid ""
"When you boot SUSE Multi-Linux Manager for the first time you need to "
"perform some initial configuration:"
msgstr "首次引导 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 时，需要执行一些初始配置："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:452
msgid "Select your keyboard layout"
msgstr "选择键盘布局"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:453
msgid "Accept the license agreement"
msgstr "接受许可协议"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:454
msgid "Select your time zone"
msgstr "选择您所在的时区"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:455
msgid "Enter the root password for the operating system"
msgstr "输入操作系统的 root 口令"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:456
msgid "The next steps need to be done as the \"root\" user:"
msgstr "后续步骤需要以“root”用户身份执行："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:457
msgid ""
"For the next step you need the registration code for the SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager Extension that you can find in the SUSE Customer Center. The same "
"code can be used for both registering SUSE Linux Micro and SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager:"
msgstr ""
"下一步操作需要使用 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 扩展的注册代码，您可在 SUSE "
"Customer Center 中找到该注册代码。此注册代码可同时用于注册 SUSE Linux Micro "
"和 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:458
msgid "Register SUSE Linux Micro:"
msgstr "注册 SUSE Linux Micro："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:459
msgid "Register SUSE Multi-Linux Manager:"
msgstr "注册 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:460
msgid ""
"The product string depends on your hardware architecture! For example, if "
"you are using SUSE Multi-Linux Manager on a 64-bit Arm system, the string is "
"\"SUSE-Manager-Server/5.0/aarch64\"."
msgstr ""
"产品字符串取决于您的硬件体系结构！例如，如果您在 64 位 Arm 系统上使用 SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager，则该字符串为“SUSE-Manager-Server/5.0/aarch64”。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:461
msgid "Reboot"
msgstr "重引导"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:462
msgid "Update the system:"
msgstr "更新系统："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:463
msgid "Unless there were no changes, reboot to apply the updates."
msgstr "除非未发生任何更改，否则请重引导系统以应用更新。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:464
msgid ""
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager is provided via a container that is managed by "
"Podman. The <literal>mgradm</literal> command handles the setup and "
"configuration for you."
msgstr ""
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 通过由 Podman 管理的容器提供。<literal>mgradm</"
"literal> 命令会为您处理设置和配置工作。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><warning><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:465
msgid ""
"It is very important that your SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server has the "
"hostname configured with a fully qualified domain name (\"FQDN\") that the "
"edge nodes you want to manage can properly resolve in your network!"
msgstr ""
"请务必为您的 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"服务器配置包含完全限定域名（简称“FQDN”）的主机名，并确保您要管理的边缘节点能"
"够在网络中正确解析该主机名！"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:466
msgid ""
"Before you install and configure the SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server "
"container, you need to prepare the additional block device that you have "
"previously added. For that, you need to know the name the virtual machine "
"has given to the device. For example, if the block device is <literal>/dev/"
"vdb</literal>, you can configure it to be used for SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"using the following command:"
msgstr ""
"在安装和配置 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server 容器之前，您需要准备好之前添加的"
"额外块设备。为此，您需要知道虚拟机为该设备分配的名称。例如，如果块设备为 "
"<literal>/dev/vdb</literal>，可使用以下命令将其配置为供 SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager 使用："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:467
msgid "Deploy SUSE Multi-Linux Manager:"
msgstr "部署 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:468
msgid ""
"Provide the password for the CA certificate. This password should be "
"different from your login passwords. You usually don’t need to enter it "
"later, but you should note it down."
msgstr "提供 CA "
"证书的口令。该口令应与您的登录口令不同。通常情况下，您之后无需输入此口令，但"
"应将其记录下来。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:469
msgid ""
"Provide the password for the \"admin\" user. This is the initial user for "
"logging into SUSE Multi-Linux Manager. You can create additional users with "
"full or restricted rights later."
msgstr ""
"提供“admin”用户的口令。这是登录 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"的初始用户。您之后可以创建具有完整权限或受限权限的其他用户。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:470
msgid "Configure SUSE Multi-Linux Manager"
msgstr "配置 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:471
msgid ""
"Once the deployment has finished, you can log into the SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager web UI using the host name you provided earlier. The initial user is "
"\"admin\". Use the password you provided in the previous step."
msgstr ""
"部署完成后，您可以使用之前提供的主机名登录 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Web "
"用户界面。初始用户为“admin”，请使用上一步设置的口令登录。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:472
msgid ""
"For the next step you need your Organization Credentials that you can find "
"on the 2nd sub-tab of the \"Users\" tab of your organization in SUSE "
"Customer Center. With those credentials, SUSE Multi-Linux Manager can "
"synchronize all the products that you have subscriptions for."
msgstr ""
"下一步需要您的组织身份凭证，这些凭证可在 SUSE Customer Center "
"中您所在组织的“用户”选项卡的第二个子选项卡中找到。通过这些身份凭证，SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager 能够同步您已订阅的所有产品。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:473
msgid "Select <literal>Admin &gt; Setup Wizard</literal>."
msgstr "选择<literal>管理 &gt; 安装向导</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:474
msgid ""
"On the <literal>Organization Credentials</literal> tab create a new "
"credential with your <literal>Username</literal> and <literal>Password</"
"literal> that you found in the SUSE Customer Center."
msgstr ""
"在<literal>组织身份凭证</literal>选项卡中，使用您在 SUSE Customer Center "
"中找到的<literal>用户名</literal>和<literal>口令</literal>创建新身份凭证。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:475
msgid ""
"Go to the next tab <literal>SUSE Products</literal>. You need to wait until "
"the first data synchronization with SUSE Customer Center has finished."
msgstr ""
"前往下一个选项卡 <literal>SUSE 产品</literal>。您需要等待与 SUSE Customer "
"Center 的首次数据同步完成。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:476
msgid ""
"Once the list is populated, you use the filter to only show \"Micro 6.1\".  "
"Check the box for SUSE Linux Micro 6.1 for the hardware architecture your "
"edge nodes will run on (<literal>x86_64</literal> or <literal>aarch64</"
"literal>)."
msgstr ""
"列表加载完毕后，使用过滤器仅显示“Micro 6.1”。选中与边缘节点运行的硬件体系结构"
"（<literal>x86_64</literal> 或 <literal>aarch64</literal>）对应的 SUSE Linux "
"Micro 6.1 复选框。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:477
msgid ""
"Click <literal>Add Products</literal>. This will add the main package "
"repository (\"channel\") for SUSE Linux Micro and automatically add the "
"channel for the SUSE Manager client tools as a sub-channel."
msgstr ""
"单击<literal>添加产品</literal>。此操作将会添加 SUSE Linux Micro "
"的主软件包储存库（即“通道”），并会自动添加 SUSE Manager "
"客户端工具的通道作为子通道。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:478
msgid ""
"Depending on your Internet connection, the first synchronization will take a "
"while. You can already start with the next steps:"
msgstr "首次同步可能需要一段时间才能完成，具体时长取决于您的互联网连接情况。您可以在"
"此期间开始执行后续步骤："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:479
msgid ""
"Under <literal>Systems &gt; System Groups</literal>, create at least one "
"group that your systems will automatically join when they are onboarded. "
"Groups are an important way of categorizing systems, so you can apply "
"configuration or actions to a whole set of systems at once. They are "
"conceptionally similar to labels in Kubernetes."
msgstr ""
"在<literal>“系统”>“系统组”</literal>下，至少创建一个组，以便系统在初始配置时"
"自动加入该组。组是对系统进行分类的重要方式，通过组可以一次性对整组系统应用配"
"置或操作。其概念类似于 Kubernetes 中的标签。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:480
msgid "Click <literal>+ Create Group</literal>"
msgstr "单击 <literal>+ 创建组</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:481
msgid "Provide a short name, e.g., \"Edge Nodes\", and long description."
msgstr "提供一个简短名称（例如“边缘节点”）和详细说明。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:482
msgid ""
"Under <literal>Systems &gt; Activation Keys</literal>, create at least one "
"activation key. Activation keys can be thought of as a configuration profile "
"that is automatically applied to systems when they are onboarded to SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager. If you want certain edge nodes to be added to different "
"groups or use different configuration, you can create separate activation "
"keys for them and use them later in Edge Image Builder to create customized "
"installation media."
msgstr ""
"在<literal>“系统”>“激活密钥”</literal>下，至少创建一个激活密钥。激活密钥可视"
"为一种配置文件，为系统进行 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"初始配置时会自动应用该配置。如果您希望特定边缘节点加入不同的组或使用不同的配"
"置，可以为它们创建单独的激活密钥，之后在 Edge Image Builder "
"中使用这些密钥来创建自定义安装媒体。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:483
msgid ""
"A typical advanced use case for activation keys would be to assign your test "
"clusters to the software channels with the latest updates and your "
"production clusters to software channels that only get those latest updates "
"once you’ve tested them in the test cluster."
msgstr ""
"激活密钥的一个典型高级使用场景是：将测试群集分配到包含最新更新的软件通道，而"
"生产群集则分配到仅会获取已在测试群集中验证过的那些最新更新的软件通道。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:484
msgid "Click <literal>+ Create Key</literal>"
msgstr "单击 <literal>+ 创建密钥</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:485
msgid ""
"Choose a short description, e.g., \"Edge Nodes\".  Provide a unique name "
"that identifies the key, e.g., \"edge-x86_64\" for your edge nodes with "
"AMD64/Intel 64 hardware architecture.  A number prefix is automatically "
"added to the key. For the default organization, the number is always \"1\". "
"If you create additional organizations in SUSE Multi-Linux Manager and "
"create keys for them, that number may differ."
msgstr ""
"输入简短说明（例如“边缘节点”），并提供一个唯一名称来标识该密钥（例如，"
"对于硬件体系结构为 AMD64/Intel 64 "
"的边缘节点，可命名为“edge-x86_64”）。密钥前面会自动添加一个数字，默认组织的前"
"缀始终为“1”；如果在 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"中创建其他组织并为其创建密钥，前缀数字可能会不同。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:486
msgid ""
"If you haven’t created any cloned software channels, you can keep the "
"setting for the Base Channel to \"SUSE Manager Default\". This will "
"automatically assign the correct SUSE update repository for your edge nodes."
msgstr ""
"如果尚未创建任何克隆的软件通道，可将“基础通道”的设置保留为“SUSE Manager "
"Default”，这会自动为边缘节点分配正确的 SUSE 更新储存库。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:487
msgid ""
"As \"Child Channel\", select the \"include recommended\" slider for the "
"hardware architecture your activation key is used for. This will add the "
"\"SUSE-Manager-Tools-For-SL-Micro-6.1\" channel."
msgstr ""
"在“子通道”中，针对激活密钥适用的硬件体系结构，选择“包括建议项”滑块，这会添加"
"“SUSE-Manager-Tools-For-SL-Micro-6.1”通道。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:488
msgid ""
"On the \"Groups\" tab, add the group you’ve created before. All nodes that "
"are onboarded using this activation key will automatically be added to that "
"group."
msgstr "在“组”选项卡中，添加之前创建的组。所有使用该激活密钥进行初始配置的节点都将自"
"动添加到该组中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:489
msgid "Create a customized installation image with Edge Image Builder"
msgstr "使用 Edge Image Builder 创建自定义安装映像"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:490
msgid ""
"To use Edge Image Builder, you only need an environment where you can start "
"a Linux-based container with podman."
msgstr "要使用 Edge Image Builder，您只需要拥有一个可通过 Podman 启动基于 Linux "
"的容器的环境。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:491
msgid ""
"For a minimal lab setup, we can actually use the same virtual machine SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager Server is running on. Please make sure that you have "
"enough disk space in the virtual machine! This is not a recommended setup "
"for production use. See <xref linkend=\"id-prerequisites-2\"/> for host "
"operating systems we have tested Edge Image Builder with."
msgstr ""
"在极简实验设置中，我们实际上可以使用运行 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"服务器的同一台虚拟机。请确保该虚拟机有充足的磁盘空间！但不建议在生产环境中采"
"用这种设置。有关我们已测试过与 Edge Image Builder 兼容的主机操作系统，"
"请参见<xref linkend=\"id-prerequisites-2\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:492
msgid "Log into your SUSE Multi-Linux Manager Server host as root."
msgstr "以 root 身份登录 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 服务器主机。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:493
msgid "Pull the Edge Image Builder container:"
msgstr "提取 Edge Image Builder 容器："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:494
msgid ""
"Create the directory <literal>/opt/eib</literal> and a sub-directory "
"<literal>base-images</literal>:"
msgstr "创建目录 <literal>/opt/eib</literal> 及其子目录 <literal>base-"
"images</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:495
msgid ""
"In this quickstart we’re using the \"self-install\" flavor of the SUSE Linux "
"Micro image. That image can later be written to a physical USB thumb drive "
"that you can use to install on physical servers. If your server has the "
"option of remote attachment of installation ISOs via a BMC (Baseboard "
"Management Controller), you can also use that approach. Finally that image "
"can also be used with most virtualization tools."
msgstr ""
"在本快速入门中，我们使用的是 SUSE Linux Micro 映像的“自安装”版本。"
"该映像之后可写入物理 USB 闪存盘，用于在物理服务器上安装系统。"
"如果服务器支持通过 BMC（基板管理控制器）远程挂接安装 "
"ISO，也可采用这种方式。此外，该映像还可与大多数虚拟化工具结合使用。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:496
msgid ""
"If you either want to preload the image directly to a physical node or "
"directly start it from a VM, you can also use the \"raw\" image flavor."
msgstr "如果需要将映像直接预加载到物理节点，或直接从虚拟机 (VM) "
"启动，也可使用“原始”版本的映像。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:497
msgid ""
"You can find those images in the SUSE Customer Center or on <link "
"xl:href=\"https://www.suse.com/download/sle-micro/\">https://www.suse.com/"
"download/sle-micro/</link>"
msgstr ""
"您可以在 SUSE Customer Center 或 <link xl:href="
"\"https://www.suse.com/download/sle-micro/\">https://www.suse.com/download/"
"sle-micro/</link> 上找到这些映像。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:498
msgid ""
"Download or copy the image <literal>SL-Micro.x86_64-6.1-Default-SelfInstall-"
"GM.install.iso</literal> to the <literal>base-images</literal> directoy and "
"name it \"slemicro.iso\"."
msgstr ""
"将映像 <literal>SL-Micro.x86_64-6.1-Default-SelfInstall-GM.install.iso</"
"literal> 下载或复制到 <literal>base-images</literal> "
"目录，并将其命名为“slemicro.iso”。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:499
msgid ""
"Building AArch64 images on an Arm-based build host is a technology preview "
"in SUSE Edge 3.4. It will most likely work, but isn’t supported yet. If you "
"want to try it out, you need to be running Podman on a 64-bit Arm machine, "
"and you need to replace \"x86_64\" in all the examples and code snippets "
"with \"aarch64\"."
msgstr ""
"在基于 Arm 的构建主机上构建 AArch64 映像属于 SUSE Edge 3.4 的技术预览功能。该"
"功能很可能可以正常运行，但目前尚未提供支持。如果您想尝试该功能，则需要在 64 "
"位 Arm 计算机上运行 Podman，并且需要将所有示例和代码段中的“x86_64”替换为“aarc"
"h64”。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:500
msgid ""
"In <literal>/opt/eib</literal>, create a file called <literal>iso-"
"definition.yaml</literal>. This is your build definition for Edge Image "
"Builder."
msgstr ""
"在 <literal>/opt/eib</literal> 中，创建一个名为 <literal>iso-"
"definition.yaml</literal> 的文件。这是用于 Edge Image Builder "
"的构建定义文件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:501
msgid ""
"Here is a simple example that installs SL Micro 6.1, sets a root password "
"and the keymap, starts the Cockpit graphical UI and registers your node to "
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager:"
msgstr ""
"下面的简单示例将会安装 SL Micro 6.1、设置 root 口令和键盘映射、启动 Cockpit "
"图形界面，并将节点注册到 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:502
msgid ""
"Edge Image Builder can also configure the network, automatically install "
"Kubernetes on the node, and even deploy applications via Helm charts. See "
"<xref linkend=\"quickstart-eib\"/> for more comprehensive examples."
msgstr ""
"Edge Image Builder 还可以配置网络、在节点上自动安装 Kubernetes，甚至通过 "
"Helm chart 部署应用程序。如需更详尽的示例，请参见<xref linkend=\"quickstart-"
"eib\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:503
msgid ""
"For <literal>baseImage</literal>, specify the actual name of the ISO in the "
"<literal>base-images</literal> directory that you want to use."
msgstr ""
"对于 <literal>baseImage</literal>，请指定要使用的 <literal>base-images</"
"literal> 目录中 ISO 的实际名称。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:504
msgid ""
"In this example, the root password would be \"root\". See <xref linkend=\"id-"
"configuring-os-users\"/> for creating password hashes for the secure "
"password you want to use."
msgstr ""
"在此示例中，root 口令为“root”。请参见<xref linkend=\"id-configuring-os-"
"users\"/>了解如何为要使用的安全口令创建口令哈希。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:505
msgid ""
"Set the keymap to the actual keyboard layout you want the system to have "
"after installation."
msgstr "将键盘映射设置为安装系统后所需的实际键盘布局。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:506
msgid ""
"We use the option <literal>noGPGCheck: true</literal> because we aren’t "
"going to provide a GPG key to check RPM packages. A comprehensive guide with "
"a more secure setup that we recommend for production use can be found in the "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/"
"release-1.3/docs/installing-packages.md\">upstream installing packages "
"guide</link>."
msgstr ""
"我们使用 <literal>noGPGCheck: true</literal> 选项，因为我们不打算提供用于检查"
" RPM 软件包的 GPG 密钥。请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/"
"edge-image-builder/blob/release-1.3/docs/installing-packages.md\">上游软件包"
"安装指南</link>，获取我们建议用于生产环境的更安全设置的综合指南。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:507
msgid ""
"As mentioned several times, your SUSE Multi-Linux Manager host requires a "
"fully qualified hostname that can be resolved in the network your edge nodes "
"will boot into."
msgstr "如前文所述， SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"主机需要一个完全限定的主机名，且在边缘节点引导至的网络中能够解析该主机名。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:508
msgid ""
"The value for <literal>activationKey</literal> needs to match the key you "
"created in SUSE Multi-Linux Manager."
msgstr ""
"<literal>activationKey</literal> 的值应与您在 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"中创建的密钥一致。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:509
msgid ""
"To build an installation image that automatically registers your edge nodes "
"to SUSE Multi-Linux Manager after installation, you also need to prepare two "
"artifacts:"
msgstr "要构建在安装后能自动将边缘节点注册到 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"的安装映像，您还需要准备两个制品："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:510
msgid ""
"the Salt minion package that installs the management agent for SUSE Multi-"
"Linux Manager"
msgstr "用于安装 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 管理代理的 Salt 受控端软件包"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:511
msgid "the CA certificate of your SUSE Multi-Linux Manager server"
msgstr "SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 服务器的 CA 证书"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:512
msgid "Download the venv-salt-minion package"
msgstr "下载 venv-salt-minion 软件包"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:513
msgid ""
"In <literal>/opt/eib</literal>, create a subdirectory <literal>rpms</"
"literal>."
msgstr "在 <literal>/opt/eib</literal> 中创建子目录 <literal>rpms</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:514
msgid ""
"Download the package <literal>venv-salt-minion</literal> from your SUSE "
"Multi-Linux Manager server into that directory. You can either get it via "
"the web UI by finding the package under <literal>Software &gt; Channel List</"
"literal> and downloading it from the SUSE-Manager-Tools …​ channel or "
"download it from the SUSE Multi-Linux Manager \"bootstrap repo\" with a tool "
"like curl:"
msgstr ""
"从 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 服务器将 <literal>venv-salt-minion</literal> "
"软件包下载到该目录。可以通过 Web UI "
"获取（在<literal>“软件”>“通道列表”</literal>中找到该软件包，并从 SUSE-"
"Manager-Tools … 通道下载），或者使用 curl 等工具从 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager "
"的“引导储存库”下载："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:515
msgid ""
"The actual package name may differ if a newer release has already been "
"released. If there are multiple packages to choose from, always pick the "
"latest."
msgstr "如果已有更新的版本发布，实际软件包名称可能会有所不同。如果有多个软件包可供选"
"择，请始终选择最新版本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:516
msgid ""
"To work around an issue documented in the <link xl:href=\"https://"
"www.suse.com/releasenotes/x86_64/multi-linux-manager/5.1/"
"index.html#_bootstrapping_sl_micro_6_1_clients\">release notes</link> for "
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager, you also need to put the latest version of the "
"build key package into the <literal>rpms</literal> directory (<literal>suse-"
"build-key-12.0-slfo.1.1_3.1.noarch.rpm</literal> at the time this "
"documentation was created). You can find it in the <literal>Software</"
"literal> section of SUSE Multi-Linux Manager via the <literal>Packages</"
"literal> tab of the Pool channel of SL Micro. There is a <literal>Download</"
"literal> button in the <literal>Details</literal> view."
msgstr ""
"为解决 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager <link xl:href=\"https://www.suse.com/"
"releasenotes/x86_64/multi-linux-manager/5.1/index.html#"
"_bootstrapping_sl_micro_6_1_clients\">发行说明</link>中记录的问题，您还需要将"
"最新版构建密钥软件包（本文档创建时为 <literal>suse-build-key-12.0-slfo.1.1_3."
"1.noarch.rpm</literal>）放入 <literal>rpms</literal> 目录。您可通过 SL Micro "
"池通道的 <literal>Packages</literal>（软件包）选项卡，在 SUSE Multi-Linux "
"Manager 的 <literal>Software</literal>（软件）部分找到该软件包。<literal>Deta"
"ils</literal>（详细信息）视图中提供了 <literal>Download</literal>（下载）按钮"
"。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:517
msgid "Download the SUSE Multi-Linux Manager CA certificate"
msgstr "下载 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager CA 证书"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:518
msgid ""
"In <literal>/opt/eib</literal>, create a subdirectory <literal>certificates</"
"literal>"
msgstr "在 <literal>/opt/eib</literal> 中创建子目录 <literal>certificates</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:519
msgid ""
"Download the CA certificate from SUSE Multi-Linux Manager into that "
"directory:"
msgstr "从 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 将 CA 证书下载到该目录："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><warning><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:520
msgid ""
"You have to rename the certificate to <literal>RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT.crt</"
"literal>. Edge Image Builder will then make sure that the certificate is "
"installed and activated on the edge node during installation."
msgstr ""
"必须将证书重命名为 <literal>RHN-ORG-TRUSTED-SSL-CERT.crt</literal>。这样，"
"Edge Image Builder 将在安装过程中确保在边缘节点上安装并激活该证书。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:521
msgid "Now you can run Edge Image Builder:"
msgstr "现在，您可以运行 Edge Image Builder："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:522
msgid ""
"If you have used a different name for your YAML definition file or want to "
"use a different version of Edge Image Builder, you need to adapt the command "
"accordingly."
msgstr "如果您为 YAML 定义文件使用了不同的名称，或者想使用其他版本的 Edge Image "
"Builder，则需要相应地调整命令。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:523
msgid ""
"After the build is finished, you’ll find the installation ISO in the "
"<literal>/opt/eib</literal> directory as <literal>eib-image.iso</literal>."
msgstr ""
"构建完成后，您可在 <literal>/opt/eib</literal> 目录中找到名为 <literal>eib-"
"image.iso</literal> 的安装 ISO。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:524
msgid ""
"That image can now be used to deploy nodes that will try to register with "
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager."
msgstr "现在，您便可使用该映像部署节点，这些节点将尝试向 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 注"
"册。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:525
msgid ""
"After the node has fully installed, you will see its key listed as "
"<literal>pending</literal> in the <literal>Salt/Keys</literal> section of "
"SUSE Multi-Linux Manager. Once you have accepted the key, the node will "
"automatically be onboarded to SUSE Multi-Liux Manager and show up in the "
"<literal>Systems</literal> list after that process is finished. It will have "
"the system group(s) assigned that you provided in the activation key."
msgstr ""
"节点完全安装后，您将在 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager 的 <literal>Salt/Keys</"
"literal> 部分看到其密钥状态显示为 <literal>pending</literal>（待处理）。接受"
"该密钥后，节点将自动加入 SUSE Multi-Linux Manager，并会在该过程完成后显示在 <"
"literal>Systems</literal>（系统）列表中。它将被分配到您在激活密钥中提供的系统"
"组。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:526
msgid ""
"You should then schedule a reboot before applying any additional "
"configuration."
msgstr "在应用任何额外配置之前，建议您安排一次重引导。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:527
msgid ""
"Note that accepting the key can be fully automated using whitelists as "
"described <link xl:href=\"https://docs.saltproject.io/en/latest/topics/"
"tutorials/autoaccept_grains.html\">here</link>."
msgstr ""
"请注意，可按照<link xl:href=\"https://docs.saltproject.io/en/latest/topics/"
"tutorials/autoaccept_grains.html\">此处</link>所述，使用白名单实现密整个密钥"
"接受过程的自动化。"

