"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/rancher-"
"extensions\">Rancher 文档</link></literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:565 l10n/source/edge.xml:896 l10n/source/edge.xml:922
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1088 l10n/source/edge.xml:1653
