#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:575
msgid "dashboard extensions create oci repository"
msgstr "仪表板扩展创建 OCI 储存库"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:576
msgid ""
"You can see that the extension repository is added to the list and is in "
"<literal>Active</literal> state."
msgstr "您会看到扩展储存库已添加到列表中，并处于 "
"<literal>Active</literal>（活动）状态。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:577
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"dashboard-extensions-repositories-"
"list.png\" width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"dashboard-extensions-repositories-list."
"png\" width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:578
msgid "dashboard extensions repositories list"
msgstr "仪表板扩展 - 储存库列表"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:579
msgid ""
"Navigate back to the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis> in the "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis> section of the navigation "
"sidebar."
msgstr ""
"导航回导航侧边栏 <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis>（配置）"
"部分的 <emphasis role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis>（扩展）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:580
msgid ""
"In the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Available</emphasis> tab you can see the "
"extensions available for installation."
msgstr "在 <emphasis role=\"strong\""
">Available</emphasis>（可用）选项卡中，可以看到可供安装的扩展。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:581
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"dashboard-extensions-available-"
"extensions.png\" width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"dashboard-extensions-available-extensions."
"png\" width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:582
msgid "dashboard extensions available extensions"
msgstr "仪表板扩展 - 可用扩展"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:583
msgid ""
"On the extension card click <literal>Install</literal> and confirm the "
"installation."
msgstr "在扩展卡片上单击 <literal>Install</literal>（安装）并确认安装。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:584
msgid ""
"Once the extension is installed Rancher UI prompts to reload the page as "
"described in the <literal><link xl:href=\"https://"
"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/rancher-"
"extensions#installing-extensions\">Installing Extensions Rancher "
"documentation page</link></literal>."
msgstr ""
"扩展安装完毕后，Rancher UI 会提示重新加载页面，具体说明请参见 <literal><link "
"xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/"
"integrations-in-rancher/rancher-extensions#installing-extensions\">Rancher 的"
"安装扩展文档页面</link></literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:585
msgid "Installing with Helm"
msgstr "使用 Helm 进行安装"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:586
msgid ""
"The extensions need to be installed in <literal>cattle-ui-plugin-system</"
"literal> namespace."
msgstr "扩展需安装在 <literal>cattle-ui-plugin-system</literal> 名称空间中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:587
msgid ""
"After an extension is installed, Rancher Dashboard UI needs to be reloaded."
msgstr "安装扩展后，需要重新加载 Rancher 仪表板 UI。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:588
msgid "Installing with Fleet"
msgstr "使用 Fleet 进行安装"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:589
msgid ""
"Installing Dashboard Extensions with Fleet requires defining a "
"<literal>gitRepo</literal> resource which points to a Git repository with "
"custom <literal>fleet.yaml</literal> bundle configuration file(s)."
msgstr ""
"使用 Fleet 安装仪表板扩展需要定义一个 <literal>gitRepo</literal> 资源，"
"该资源指向包含自定义 <literal>fleet.yaml</literal> 捆绑包配置文件的 Git "
"储存库。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:590
msgid ""
"The <literal>releaseName</literal> property is required and needs to match "
"the extension name to get the extension correctly installed."
msgstr "必须指定 <literal>releaseName</literal> "
"属性，而且它需要与扩展名称匹配，才能正确安装扩展。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:591
msgid ""
"For more information, see <xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/> and the "
"<literal><link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples\">fleet-"
"examples</link></literal> repository."
msgstr ""
"有关详细信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>和 <literal><link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples\">fleet-"
"examples</link></literal> 储存库。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:592
msgid ""
"Once the Extensions are installed they are listed in <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis> section under <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Installed</emphasis> tabs. Since they are not installed via "
"Apps/Marketplace, they are marked with <literal>Third-Party</literal> label."
msgstr ""
"安装扩展后，它们将列在 <emphasis role=\"strong\""
">Installed</emphasis>（已安装）选项卡下的 <emphasis role=\"strong\""
">Extensions</emphasis>（扩展）部分中。由于它们不是通过 Apps/Marketplace "
"安装的，因此带有 <literal>Third-Party</literal>（第三方）标签。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:593
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"installed-dashboard-extensions.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"installed-dashboard-extensions.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:594
msgid "installed dashboard extensions"
msgstr "已安装的仪表板扩展"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:595 l10n/source/edge.xml:4246
msgid "KubeVirt Dashboard Extension"
msgstr "KubeVirt 仪表板扩展"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:596
msgid ""
"KubeVirt Extension provides basic virtual machine management for Rancher "
"dashboard UI. Its capabilities are described in <xref linkend=\"kubevirt-"
"dashboard-extension-usage\"/>."
msgstr ""
"KubeVirt 扩展为 Rancher 仪表板 UI 提供基本虚拟机管理。<xref linkend"
"=\"kubevirt-dashboard-extension-usage\"/>中介绍了其功能。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:597
msgid "Akri Dashboard Extension"
msgstr "Akri 仪表板扩展"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:598
msgid ""
"Akri is a Kubernetes Resource Interface that lets you easily expose "
"heterogeneous leaf devices (such as IP cameras and USB devices) as resources "
"in a Kubernetes cluster, while also supporting the exposure of embedded "
"hardware resources such as GPUs and FPGAs. Akri continually detects nodes "
"that have access to these devices and schedules workloads based on them."
msgstr ""
"Akri 是一个 Kubernetes 资源接口，让您可以轻松地将异构叶设备（例如 IP "
"摄像头和 USB 设备）公开为 Kubernetes 群集中的资源，同时还支持公开 GPU 和 "
"FPGA 等嵌入式硬件资源。Akri "
"会持续检测有权访问这些设备的节点，并根据这些节点调度工作负载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:599 l10n/source/edge.xml:872
msgid ""
"Akri Dashboard Extension allows you to use Rancher Dashboard user interface "
"to manage and monitor leaf devices and run workloads once these devices are "
"discovered."
msgstr "Akri 仪表板扩展允许您使用 Rancher "
"仪表板用户界面来管理和监控叶设备，并在发现这些设备后运行工作负载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:600
msgid ""
"Extension capabilities are further described in <xref linkend=\"akri-"
"dashboard-extension-usage\"/>."
msgstr "<xref linkend=\"akri-dashboard-extension-usage\"/>中详细介绍了扩展功能。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:601
msgid "Rancher Turtles"
msgstr "Rancher Turtles"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:602
msgid ""
"See Rancher Turtles documentation at <link xl:href=\"https://"
"documentation.suse.com/cloudnative/cluster-api/\">https://"
"documentation.suse.com/cloudnative/cluster-api/</link>"
msgstr ""
"请参见 Rancher Turtles 文档，网址为：<link xl:href="
"\"https://documentation.suse.com/cloudnative/cluster-api/\">https://"
"documentation.suse.com/cloudnative/cluster-api/</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><blockquote><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:603
msgid ""
"Rancher Turtles is a Kubernetes Operator that provides integration between "
"Rancher Manager and Cluster API (CAPI) with the aim of bringing full CAPI "
"support to Rancher"
msgstr ""
"Rancher Turtles 是一个 Kubernetes 操作器，它提供 Rancher Manager 与 Cluster "
"API (CAPI) 之间的集成，旨在为 Rancher 添加全面的 CAPI 支持"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:604
msgid "Key Features of Rancher Turtles"
msgstr "Rancher Turtles 的主要功能"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:605
msgid ""
"Automatically import CAPI clusters into Rancher, by installing the Rancher "
"Cluster Agent in CAPI provisioned clusters."
msgstr "通过在 CAPI 置备的群集中安装 Rancher 群集代理，自动将 CAPI 群集导入 Rancher。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:606
msgid ""
"Install and configure CAPI controller dependencies via the <link "
"xl:href=\"https://cluster-api-operator.sigs.k8s.io/\">CAPI Operator</link>."
msgstr ""
"通过 <link xl:href=\"https://cluster-api-operator.sigs.k8s.io/\">CAPI "
"操作器</link>安装并配置 CAPI 控制器依赖项。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:607
msgid "Rancher Turtles use in SUSE Edge"
msgstr "Rancher Turtles 在 SUSE Edge 中的使用"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:608
msgid ""
"The SUSE Edge stack provides a helm wrapper chart which installs Rancher "
"Turtles with a specific configuration that enables:"
msgstr "SUSE Edge 堆栈提供了一个 Helm 封装 chart，该 chart 可使用特定配置安装 "
"Rancher Turtles，以启用："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:609
msgid "Core CAPI controller components"
msgstr "核心 CAPI 控制器组件"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:610
msgid "RKE2 Control Plane and Bootstrap provider components"
msgstr "RKE2 控制平面和引导提供程序组件"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:611
msgid ""
"Metal3 (<xref linkend=\"components-metal3\"/>) infrastructure provider "
"components"
msgstr "Metal3（<xref linkend=\"components-metal3\"/>）基础架构提供程序组件"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:612
msgid ""
"Only the default providers installed via the wrapper chart are supported - "
"alternative Control Plane, Bootstrap and Infrastructure providers are not "
"currently supported as part of the SUSE Edge stack."
msgstr "仅支持通过封装 chart 安装的默认提供程序 - 目前不支持替代的控制平面、"
"引导和基础架构提供程序作为 SUSE Edge 堆栈的一部分。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:613
msgid "Installing Rancher Turtles"
msgstr "安装 Rancher Turtles"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:614
msgid ""
"Rancher Turtles may be installed by following the Metal3 Quickstart (<xref "
"linkend=\"quickstart-metal3\"/>) guide, or the Management Cluster (<xref "
"linkend=\"atip-management-cluster\"/>) documentation."
msgstr ""
"可按照 Metal3 快速入门（<xref linkend=\"quickstart-metal3\""
"/>）指南或管理群集（<xref linkend=\"atip-management-cluster\"/>）"
"文档所述安装 Rancher Turtles。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:617
msgid ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://cluster-api.sigs.k8s.io/\">Cluster API Book</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://cluster-api.sigs.k8s.io/\">《Cluster API "
"Book》</link>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:618 l10n/source/edge.xml:1789 l10n/source/edge.xml:1800
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1829 l10n/source/edge.xml:2338
msgid "Fleet"
msgstr "Fleet"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:619
msgid ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io\">Fleet</link> is a container "
"management and deployment engine designed to offer users more control on the "
"local cluster and constant monitoring through GitOps. Fleet focuses not only "
"on the ability to scale, but it also gives users a high degree of control "
"and visibility to monitor exactly what is installed on the cluster."
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io\">Fleet</link> "
"是一个容器管理和部署引擎，旨在让用户更好地控制本地群集，并通过 GitOps "
"进行持续监控。Fleet "
"不仅注重缩放能力，而且还为用户提供很高的控制度和可见性，以准确监控群集上安装"
"的组件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:620
msgid ""
"Fleet can manage deployments from Git of raw Kubernetes YAML, Helm charts, "
"Kustomize, or any combination of the three. Regardless of the source, all "
"resources are dynamically turned into Helm charts, and Helm is used as the "
"engine to deploy all resources in the cluster. As a result, users can enjoy "
"a high degree of control, consistency and auditability of their clusters."
msgstr ""
"Fleet 可以管理通过原始 Kubernetes YAML、Helm chart、Kustomize 的 Git "
"软件包或这三者的任意组合完成的部署。无论来源是什么，所有资源都会动态转换为 "
"Helm chart，并使用 Helm "
"作为引擎在群集中部署所有资源。因此，用户可以获享很高的群集控制度、一致性和可"
"审计性。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:621
msgid ""
"For information about how Fleet works, see <link xl:href=\"https://"
"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/fleet/"
"architecture\">Fleet Architecture</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关 Fleet 工作原理的信息，请参见 <link xl:href=\"https://"
"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.12/integrations-in-rancher/fleet/"
"architecture\">Fleet Architecture</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:622
msgid "Installing Fleet with Helm"
msgstr "使用 Helm 安装 Fleet"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:623
msgid ""
"Fleet comes built-in to Rancher, but it can be also <link xl:href=\"https://"
"fleet.rancher.io/installation\">installed</link> as a standalone application "
"on any Kubernetes cluster using Helm."
msgstr ""
"Fleet 已内置于 Rancher 中，但您也可以使用 Helm 将 Fleet <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/installation\">安装</link>为任何 Kubernetes "
"群集上的独立应用程序。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:624
msgid "Using Fleet with Rancher"
msgstr "使用 Rancher 中的 Fleet"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:625
msgid ""
"Rancher uses Fleet to deploy applications across managed clusters. "
"Continuous delivery with Fleet introduces GitOps at scale, designed to "
"manage applications running on large numbers of clusters."
msgstr ""
"Rancher 使用 Fleet 在受管群集中部署应用程序。Fleet "
"的持续交付功能引入了大规模 GitOps，旨在管理在大量群集上运行的应用程序。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:626
msgid ""
"Fleet shines as an integrated part of Rancher. Clusters managed with Rancher "
"automatically get the Fleet agent deployed as part of the installation/"
"import process and the cluster is immediately available to be managed by "
"Fleet."
msgstr ""
"Fleet 作为 Rancher 的集成部分优势显著：使用 Rancher 管理的群集会在安装/"
"导入过程中自动由 Fleet 代理部署，并且之后群集立即便能由 Fleet 管理。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:627
msgid "Accessing Fleet in the Rancher UI"
msgstr "在 Rancher UI 中访问 Fleet"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:628
msgid ""
"Fleet comes preinstalled in Rancher and is managed by the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Continuous Delivery</emphasis> option in the Rancher UI."
msgstr ""
"Rancher 中预安装了 Fleet，可通过 Rancher UI 中的 <emphasis role=\"strong\""
">Continuous Delivery</emphasis>（持续交付）选项进行管理。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:629
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-dashboard.png\" width=\"100%\"/> </"
"imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-dashboard.png\" width=\"100%\"/> "
"</imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:630
msgid "fleet dashboard"
msgstr "Fleet 仪表板"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:631
msgid "Continuous Delivery section consists of following items:"
msgstr "“Continuous Delivery”（持续交付）部分包括以下项目："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:632
msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard（仪表板）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:633
msgid ""
"An overview page of all GitOps repositories across all workspaces. Only the "
"workspaces with repositories are displayed."
msgstr "所有工作空间中所有 GitOps 储存库的概览页面。仅显示包含储存库的工作空间。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:634
msgid "Git repos"
msgstr "Git repos（Git 储存库）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:635
msgid ""
"A list of GitOps repositories in the selected workspace. Select the active "
"workspace using the dropdown list at the top of the page."
msgstr "所选工作空间中的 GitOps 储存库列表。使用页面顶部的下拉列表选择活动工作空间。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:636
msgid "Clusters"
msgstr "Clusters（群集）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:637
msgid ""
"A list of managed clusters. By default, all Rancher-managed clusters are "
"added to the <literal>fleet-default</literal> workspace. <literal>fleet-"
"local</literal> workspace includes the local (management) cluster. From "
"here, it is possible to <literal>Pause</literal> or <literal>Force update</"
"literal> the clusters or move the cluster into another workspace. Editing "
"the cluster allows to update labels and annotations used for grouping the "
"clusters."
msgstr ""
"受管群集列表。默认情况下，Rancher 管理的所有群集都会添加到 <literal>fleet-"
"default</literal> 工作空间。<literal>fleet-local</literal> "
"工作空间包含本地（管理）群集。在此处可以<literal>暂停</literal>或<literal>强"
"制更新</literal>群集，或者将群集移动到另一个工作空间。可以通过编辑群集来更新"
"用于群集分组的标签和注解。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:638
msgid "Cluster groups"
msgstr "Cluster groups（群集组）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:639
msgid ""
"This section allows custom grouping of the clusters within the workspace "
"using selectors."
msgstr "在此部分，可以使用选择器对工作空间内的群集进行自定义分组。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:640
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Advanced（高级）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:641
msgid ""
"The \"Advanced\" section allows to manage workspaces and other related Fleet "
"resources."
msgstr "在“Advanced”（高级）部分可以管理工作空间和其他相关 Fleet 资源。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:642
msgid ""
"Example of installing KubeVirt with Rancher and Fleet using Rancher dashboard"
msgstr "使用 Rancher 仪表板通过 Rancher 和 Fleet 安装 KubeVirt 的示例"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:643
msgid ""
"Create a Git repository containing the <literal>fleet.yaml</literal> file:"
msgstr "创建包含 <literal>fleet.yaml</literal> 文件的 Git 储存库："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:644
msgid ""
"In the Rancher dashboard, navigate to <emphasis role=\"strong\">☰ &gt; "
"Continuous Delivery &gt; Git Repos</emphasis> and click <literal>Add "
"Repository</literal>."
msgstr ""
"在 Rancher 仪表板中，导航到 <emphasis role=\"strong\">☰ &gt; Continuous "
"Delivery（持续交付）&gt; Git repos（Git 储存库）</emphasis>，然后单击 "
"<literal>Add Repository</literal>（添加储存库）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:645
msgid ""
"The Repository creation wizard guides through creation of the Git repo. "
"Provide <emphasis role=\"strong\">Name</emphasis>, <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Repository URL</emphasis> (referencing the Git repository "
"created in the previous step) and select the appropriate branch or revision. "
"In the case of a more complex repository, specify <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Paths</emphasis> to use multiple directories in a single "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"储存库创建向导将指导您完成 Git 储存库创建步骤。提供<emphasis role=\"strong\""
">名称</emphasis>、<emphasis role=\"strong\">储存库 URL</emphasis>（"
"引用上一步骤中创建的 Git "
"储存库），并选择适当的分支或修订版。对于较复杂的储存库，请指定<emphasis role="
"\"strong\">路径</emphasis>以便在单个储存库中使用多个目录。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:646
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-create-repo1.png\" width=\"100%\"/> "
"</imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-create-repo1.png\" width=\"100%\"/> "
"</imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:647
msgid "fleet create repo1"
msgstr "Fleet - 创建储存库 1"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:648
msgid "Click <literal>Next</literal>."
msgstr "单击 <literal>Next</literal>（下一步）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:649
msgid ""
"In the next step, you can define where the workloads will get deployed. "
"Cluster selection offers several basic options: you can select no clusters, "
"all clusters, or directly choose a specific managed cluster or cluster group "
"(if defined). The \"Advanced\" option allows to directly edit the selectors "
"via YAML."
msgstr ""
"在下一步骤中，可以定义工作负载的部署位置。在群集选择方面，可以使用多个基本选"
"项：可以不选择任何群集、选择所有群集，或者直接选择特定的受管群集或群集组（如"
"果已定义）。“Advanced”（高级）选项允许通过 YAML 直接编辑选择器。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:650
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-create-repo2.png\" width=\"100%\"/> "
"</imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-create-repo2.png\" width=\"100%\"/> "
"</imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:651
msgid "fleet create repo2"
msgstr "Fleet - 创建储存库 2"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:652
msgid ""
"Click <literal>Create</literal>. The repository gets created. From now on, "
"the workloads are installed and kept in sync on the clusters matching the "
"repository definition."
msgstr ""
"单击 "
"<literal>Create</literal>（创建）。系统即会创建储存库。从现在起，工作负载将在"
"与储存库定义匹配的群集上安装并保持同步。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:653
msgid "Debugging and troubleshooting"
msgstr "调试和查错"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:654
msgid ""
"The \"Advanced\" navigation section provides overviews of lower-level Fleet "
"resources. <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-bundle-stages\">A "
"bundle</link> is an internal resource used for the orchestration of "
"resources from Git. When a Git repo is scanned, it produces one or more "
"bundles."
msgstr ""
"“Advanced”（高级）导航部分提供了低层级 Fleet 资源的概览。<link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-bundle-stages\">捆绑包</link>是一个内部资源，"
"用于编排 Git 中的资源。扫描 Git 储存库时，会生成一个或多个捆绑包。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:655
msgid ""
"To find bundles relevant to a specific repository, go to the Git repo detail "
"page and click the <literal>Bundles</literal> tab."
msgstr "要查找与特定储存库相关的捆绑包，请转到 Git 储存库细节页面，并单击 "
"<literal>Bundles</literal>（捆绑包）选项卡。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:656
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-repo-bundles.png\" width=\"100%\"/> "
"</imageobject>"
msgstr ""
