#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:943
msgid ""
"A core requirement of deploying and using SUSE Storage is the installation "
"of the <literal>open-iscsi</literal> package and the <literal>iscsid</"
"literal> daemon running on all Kubernetes nodes.  This is necessary, since "
"Longhorn relies on <literal>iscsiadm</literal> on the host to provide "
"persistent volumes to Kubernetes."
msgstr ""
"要部署并使用 SUSE Storage，需满足的一项核心要求是在所有 Kubernetes "
"节点上安装 <literal>open-iscsi</literal> 软件包并运行 <literal>iscsid</"
"literal> 守护程序。之所以有此要求，是因为 Longhorn 依赖于主机上的 "
"<literal>iscsiadm</literal> 来为 Kubernetes 提供持久卷。"

