"\"https://github.com/k3s-io/helm-controller/\">helm-controller</link> "
"为它们创建的资源。有关详细信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-"
"controller-how-track-helm\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
