#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1303
msgid ""
"The <literal>lastSuccessfulReleaseVersion</literal> property points to the "
"<literal>releaseVersion</literal> that is specified in the Upgrade Plan’s "
