"by the Upgrade Controller once the upgrade process is successful.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>lastSuccessfulReleaseVersion</literal> 属性指向升级计划配置中指定的 "
"<literal>releaseVersion</literal>。<emphasis>升级过程成功后，升级控制器会将此"
"属性添加至升级计划的状态。</emphasis>"

