#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1368
msgid "MetalLB on K3s (using Layer 3 Mode)"
msgstr "K3s 上的 MetalLB（使用第 3 层模式）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1370
msgid ""
"In this guide, we demonstrate how to deploy MetalLB in layer 3 (L3) BGP mode."
msgstr "本指南将演示如何在第 3 层 (L3) BGP 模式下部署 MetalLB。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1375
msgid ""
"Supports Multiple Protocols: MetalLB supports both Layer 2 and Layer 3 BGP "
"(Border Gateway Protocol) modes, providing flexibility for different network "
"architectures and requirements."
msgstr ""
"支持多种协议：MetalLB 支持第 2 层和第 3 层 BGP（边界网关协议）模式，提供了很"
"大的灵活性，适合不同的网络架构并可满足不同的要求。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1380
msgid "MetalLB on K3s (using L3)"
msgstr "K3s 上的 MetalLB（使用 L3）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1381
msgid ""
"In this quick start, L3 mode is used.  This means that we need to have "
"neighboring router(s) with BGP capabilities within the network range."
msgstr "本快速入门中使用 L3 模式，这意味着网络范围内需要有支持 BGP 功能的相邻路由器。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1384
msgid "Router(s) on the network that support the BGP protocol."
msgstr "网络中支持 BGP 协议的路由器。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1385
msgid ""
"A free IP address within the network range for the service. In this example "
"<literal>192.168.10.100</literal>"
msgstr "网络范围内用于服务的空闲 IP 地址，本示例中为 "
"<literal>192.168.10.100</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1386
msgid ""
"You must make sure this IP address is unassigned.  In a DHCP environment "
"this address must not be part of the DHCP pool to avoid dual assignments."
msgstr "您必须确保此 IP 地址未被分配。在 DHCP 环境中，该地址不得属于 DHCP 池，以避免"
"重复分配。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1387
msgid "Configuration to Advertise Service IP Addresses"
msgstr "配置服务 IP 地址通告"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1388
msgid ""
"Out of the box BGP advertises a Service IP address to all the peers that are "
"configured. These peers, which are usually routers, will receive a route for "
"each Service IP address with a 32 bit network mask. In this examlple we will "
"use an FRR based router and is on the same network as our cluster. We will "
"then use MetalLB’s BGP capability to advertise a service to that FRR based "
"router."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，BGP 会向所有已配置的对等方通告服务 IP 地址。这些对等方（通常是路"
"由器）会收到每个服务 IP 地址的路由，且网络掩码为 32 位。在本示例中，我们将使"
"用与群集处于同一网络的基于 FRR 的路由器，然后利用 MetalLB 的 BGP 功能向该基于"
" FRR 的路由器通告服务。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1392
msgid ""
"At this point, the installation is complete. Create an "
"<literal>IPAddressPool</literal>:"
