#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1546
msgid "Pull the latest Kiwi builder image from the SUSE Registry:"
msgstr "从 SUSE 仓库提取最新的 Kiwi 构建器映像："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1547
msgid "Building the Default Image"
msgstr "构建默认映像"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1548
msgid ""
"This is the default behavior of the Kiwi image container if no arguments are "
"provided during the container image run. The following command runs "
"<literal>podman</literal> with two directories mapped to the container:"
msgstr ""
"如果运行容器映像时未提供任何参数，这就是 Kiwi 映像容器的默认行为。"
