"<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/> 通过创建 <literal>HelmChart</literal> "
"资源并利用 <link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io/helm\">RKE2</link>/<link "
"xl:href=\"https://docs.k3s.io/helm\">K3s</link> Helm 集成功能引入的 <literal"
">helm-controller</literal> 来部署 Helm chart。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2227 l10n/source/edge.xml:2723
msgid ""
"To ensure that a Helm chart deployed via <literal>EIB</literal> is "
"successfully upgraded, users need to do an upgrade over the respective "
"<literal>HelmChart</literal> resources."
