"通过 <literal>EIB</literal> 部署的 Helm chart 由名为 <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/tree/release-3.4.0/fleets/day2/eib-"
"charts-upgrader\">eib-charts-upgrader</link> 的 <literal>Fleet</literal> 执行"
