#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3307
msgid ""
"Isolate the cores 1-30 and 33-62. <literal>domain</literal> indicates these "
"CPUs are part of isolation domain. <literal>nohz</literal> enables tickless "
"operation on these isolated CPUs when they are idle, to reduce "
"interruptions. <literal>managed_irq</literal> isolates pinned CPUs from "
"being targeted by IRQs. This contemplates <literal>irqaffinity=0-7</"
"literal>, which already directs mosts IRQs to the housekeeping cores."
msgstr ""
"隔离核心 1-30 和 33-62。<literal>domain</literal> 表示这些 CPU "
"属于隔离域。<literal>nohz</literal> 在这些隔离的 CPU "
"空闲时启用无节拍操作，以减少中断。<literal>managed_irq</literal> 使绑定的 "
"CPU 免受 IRQ 干扰。这考虑了 <literal>irqaffinity=0-7</literal>，它已将大多数 "
"IRQ 定向到系统管理核心。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3308 l10n/source/edge.xml:3869
msgid "skew_tick"
msgstr "skew_tick"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3309 l10n/source/edge.xml:3870
msgid "1"
msgstr "1"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3310
msgid ""
"This option allows the kernel to skew the timer interrupts across the "
"isolated CPUs."
msgstr "此选项允许内核在隔离的 CPU 之间错开定时器中断。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3311 l10n/source/edge.xml:3872
msgid "nohz"
msgstr "nohz"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3312 l10n/source/edge.xml:3443
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3464 l10n/source/edge.xml:3873
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3891
msgid "on"
msgstr "on"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3313
msgid ""
"When enabled, kernel’s periodic timer interrupt (the 'tick') will stop on "
"any CPU core that is idle. This primary benefits the housekeeping CPUs "
"(<literal>0,31,32,63</literal>). This conserves power and reduces "
"unnecessary wake-ups on those general-purpose cores."
msgstr ""
"启用后，内核的周期性定时器中断（即“节拍”）将在任何空闲的 CPU 核心上停止。"
"这主要有益于系统管理 "
"CPU（<literal>0、31、32、63</literal>）。这可节省电力并减少这些通用核心上不必"
"要的唤醒。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3314 l10n/source/edge.xml:3875
msgid "nohz_full"
msgstr "nohz_full"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3315 l10n/source/edge.xml:3318
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3876 l10n/source/edge.xml:3879
msgid "1-30,33-62"
msgstr "1-30,33-62"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3316
msgid ""
"For the isolated cores, this stops the tick and it does so even when the CPU "
"is running a single active task. It means it makes the CPU run in full "
"tickless mode (or 'dyntick'). The kernel will only deliver timer interrupts "
"when they are actually needed."
msgstr ""
"对于隔离的核心，这会停止节拍，即使 CPU 运行单个活动任务，也不例外。"
"这意味着它使 CPU "
"以完全无节拍模式（或“动态节拍”）运行。内核仅在实际需要时才会传递定时器中断。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3317 l10n/source/edge.xml:3878
msgid "rcu_nocbs"
msgstr "rcu_nocbs"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3319
msgid ""
"This option offloads the RCU callback processing from specified CPU cores."
msgstr "此选项会将 RCU 回调处理从指定的 CPU 核心卸载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3320
msgid "rcu_nocb_poll"
msgstr "rcu_nocb_poll"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3321
msgid ""
"When this option is set, no-RCU-callback CPUs will regularly 'poll' to see "
"if callback handling is required, rather than being explicitly woken up by "
"other CPUs. This can reduce the interrupt overhead."
msgstr "如果设置此选项，无 RCU 回调的 CPU 将定期“轮询”以确定是否需要处理回调，"
"而不是由其他 CPU 显式唤醒。这可以减少中断开销。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3322 l10n/source/edge.xml:3881
msgid "irqaffinity"
msgstr "irqaffinity"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3323 l10n/source/edge.xml:3882
msgid "0,31,32,63"
msgstr "0,31,32,63"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3324
msgid ""
"This option allows the kernel to run the interrupts to the housekeeping "
"cores."
msgstr "此选项允许内核在系统管理核心上运行中断。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3325 l10n/source/edge.xml:3884
msgid "idle"
msgstr "idle"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3326 l10n/source/edge.xml:3885
msgid "poll"
msgstr "poll"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3327
msgid ""
"This minimizes the latency of exiting the idle state, but at the cost of "
"keeping the CPU running at full speed in the idle thread."
msgstr "最大限度减少因退出空闲状态造成的延迟，但代价是 CPU "
"在空闲线程中也要保持全速运行。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3328 l10n/source/edge.xml:3904
msgid "nmi_watchdog"
msgstr "nmi_watchdog"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
