#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3377
msgid ""
"Using the Bond CNI with SR-IOV is fairly straight forward. For more details "
"on how to set up SR-IOV, see <xref linkend=\"sriov\"/>. As described there, "
"you have to create <literal>SriovNetworkNodePolicies</literal> that defines "
"<literal>resourceNames</literal>, as well as number of virtual functions and "
"such. The <literal>resourceNames</literal> are being used by the "
"<literal>SriovNetwork</literal> which is used as interfaces in the pod "
"definition. The bond definition is exactly the same as for the MACVLAN and "
"host device cases."
msgstr ""
"将 Bond CNI 与 SR-IOV 结合使用的操作相当简单。有关如何设置 SR-IOV 的详细信息"
"，请参见<xref linkend=\"sriov\"/>。如前文所述，您需要创建 "
"<literal>SriovNetworkNodePolicies</literal>，在其中定义 "
"<literal>resourceNames</literal> 以及虚拟功能的数量等。"
"<literal>resourceNames</literal> 供 <literal>SriovNetwork</literal> 使用，"
"SriovNetwork 在 Pod 定义中用作接口。绑定定义与 MACVLAN 和 Host Device 场景完"
"全相同。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3378
msgid ""
"Bond CNI with SR-IOV is only applicable to SRIOV Virtual Functions (VF) "
"using the kernel driver. Userspace driver VFs - such as those used in DPDK "
"workloads - can not be bonded with the Bond CNI."
msgstr ""
"Bond CNI 与 SR-IOV 结合使用这种方式仅适用于使用内核驱动程序的 SRIOV 虚拟功能"
"。用户空间驱动程序 VF（如 DPDK 工作负载中使用的 VF）无法通过 Bond CNI 进行绑"
"定。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3380
msgid ""
"SR-IOV allows a device, such as a network adapter, to separate access to its "
"resources among various <literal>PCIe</literal> hardware functions.  There "
"are different ways to deploy <literal>SR-IOV</literal>, and here, we show "
"two different options:"
msgstr ""
"SR-IOV 允许网络适配器等设备在各种 <literal>PCIe</literal> "
"硬件功能之间分隔对其资源的访问。可以通过多种方式部署 <literal>SR-"
"IOV</literal>，本节将介绍两种不同的方式："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3381
msgid ""
"Option 1: using the <literal>SR-IOV</literal> CNI device plug-ins and a "
"config map to configure it properly."
msgstr "方式 1：使用 <literal>SR-IOV</literal> CNI 设备插件和配置映射来正确配置 SR-"
"IOV。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3382
msgid ""
"Option 2 (recommended): using the <literal>SR-IOV</literal> Helm chart from "
"Rancher Prime to make this deployment easy."
msgstr ""
"方式 2（建议）：使用 Rancher Prime 中的 <literal>SR-IOV</literal> Helm chart "
"来轻松完成此部署。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3383
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Option 1 - Installation of SR-IOV CNI device plug-"
"ins and a config map to configure it properly</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">方式 1 - 安装 SR-IOV CNI "
"设备插件并准备配置映射来正确配置 SR-IOV</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3384
msgid "Prepare the config map for the device plug-in"
msgstr "为设备插件准备配置映射"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3385
msgid ""
"Get the information to fill the config map from the <literal>lspci</literal> "
"command:"
msgstr "使用 <literal>lspci</literal> 命令获取用于填充配置映射的信息："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3386
msgid ""
"The config map consists of a <literal>JSON</literal> file that describes "
"devices using filters to discover, and creates groups for the interfaces.  "
"The key is understanding filters and groups. The filters are used to "
"discover the devices and the groups are used to create the interfaces."
msgstr ""
"配置映射由一个 <literal>JSON</literal> "
"文件组成，该文件描述通过过滤器发现的设备，以及创建接口组所需的信息。此处的关"
"键在于理解过滤器和组。过滤器用于发现设备，组用于创建接口。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3387
msgid "It could be possible to set filters:"
msgstr "可以设置过滤器："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3388
msgid "vendorID: <literal>8086</literal> (Intel)"
msgstr "vendorID：<literal>8086</literal> (Intel)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3389
msgid "deviceID: <literal>0d5c</literal> (Accelerator card)"
msgstr "deviceID：<literal>0d5c</literal>（加速卡）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3390
msgid "driver: <literal>vfio-pci</literal> (driver)"
msgstr "driver：<literal>vfio-pci</literal>（驱动程序）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3391
msgid "pfNames: <literal>p2p1</literal> (physical interface name)"
msgstr "pfNames：<literal>p2p1</literal>（物理接口名称）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3392
msgid ""
"It could be possible to also set filters to match more complex interface "
"syntax, for example:"
msgstr "还可以设置过滤器来匹配更复杂的接口语法，例如："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3393
msgid ""
"pfNames: <literal>[\"eth1#1,2,3,4,5,6\"]</literal> or <literal>[eth1#1-6]</"
"literal> (physical interface name)"
msgstr ""
"pfNames：<literal>[\"eth1#1,2,3,4,5,6\"]</literal> 或 <literal>[eth1#1-6]"
"</literal>（物理接口名称）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3394
msgid ""
"Related to the groups, we could create a group for the <literal>FEC</"
"literal> card and another group for the <literal>Intel</literal> card, even "
"creating a prefix depending on our use case:"
msgstr ""
"至于组，我们可为 <literal>FEC</literal> 卡创建一个组，为 <literal>Intel</"
"literal> 卡创建另一个组，甚至可以根据具体使用场景创建一个前缀："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3395
msgid "resourceName: <literal>pci_sriov_net_bh_dpdk</literal>"
msgstr "resourceName：<literal>pci_sriov_net_bh_dpdk</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3396
msgid "resourcePrefix: <literal>Rancher.io</literal>"
msgstr "resourcePrefix：<literal>Rancher.io</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3397
msgid ""
"There are a lot of combinations to discover and create the resource group to "
"allocate some <literal>VFs</literal> to the pods."
msgstr "可以发现许多组合，并创建资源组来为 Pod 分配一些 <literal>VF</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3398
msgid ""
"For more information about the filters and groups, visit <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/k8snetworkplumbingwg/sriov-network-device-"
"plugin\">sr-iov network device plug-in</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关过滤器和组的详细信息，请访问 <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/k8snetworkplumbingwg/sriov-network-device-plugin\">sr-"
"iov 网络设备插件</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3399
msgid ""
"After setting the filters and groups to match the interfaces depending on "
"the hardware and the use case, the following config map shows an example to "
"be used:"
msgstr "根据硬件和使用场景设置用于匹配接口的过滤器和组后，下面的配置映射展示了一个可"
"使用的示例："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3400
msgid ""
"Prepare the <literal>daemonset</literal> file to deploy the device plug-in."
msgstr "准备 <literal>daemonset</literal> 文件以部署设备插件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3401
msgid ""
"The device plug-in supports several architectures (<literal>arm</literal>, "
"<literal>amd</literal>, <literal>ppc64le</literal>), so the same file can be "
"used for different architectures deploying several <literal>daemonset</"
"literal> for each architecture."
msgstr ""
"设备插件支持多种体系结构（<literal>arm</literal>、<literal>amd</literal>、<li"
"teral>ppc64le</literal>），因此同一文件可用于不同的体系结构，"
"以便为每个体系结构部署多个 <literal>daemonset</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3402
msgid ""
"After applying the config map and the <literal>daemonset</literal>, the "
"device plug-in will be deployed and the interfaces will be discovered and "
"available for the pods."
msgstr "应用配置映射和 <literal>daemonset</literal> 后，将部署设备插件，"
"发现接口并将其提供给 Pod 使用。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3403
msgid ""
"Check the interfaces discovered and available in the nodes to be used by the "
"pods:"
msgstr "检查节点中发现的且可供 Pod 使用的接口："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3404
msgid ""
"The <literal>FEC</literal> is <literal>intel.com/intel_fec_5g</literal> and "
"the value is 1."
msgstr ""
"<literal>FEC</literal> 为 <literal>intel.com/intel_fec_5g</literal>，值为 1。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3405
msgid ""
"The <literal>VF</literal> is <literal>intel.com/intel_sriov_odu</literal> or "
"<literal>intel.com/intel_sriov_oru</literal> if you deploy it with a device "
"plug-in and the config map without Helm charts."
msgstr ""
"如果您部署 SR-IOV 时使用了设备插件和配置映射，但未使用 Helm chart，则 "
"<literal>VF</literal> 为 <literal>intel.com/intel_sriov_odu</literal> 或 "
"<literal>intel.com/intel_sriov_oru</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3406
msgid ""
"If there are no interfaces here, it makes little sense to continue because "
"the interface will not be available for pods. Review the config map and "
"filters to solve the issue first."
msgstr "如果此处没有接口，则继续操作就意义不大，因为 Pod "
"没有可用的接口。请先检查配置映射和过滤器来解决问题。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3407
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Option 2 (recommended) - Installation using "
"Rancher using Helm chart for SR-IOV CNI and device plug-ins</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">方式 2（建议）- 使用 Rancher 和 Helm chart 安装 SR-"
"IOV CNI 和设备插件</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3408
msgid "Get Helm if not present:"
msgstr "获取 Helm（如果没有）："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3409
msgid "Install SR-IOV."
msgstr "安装 SR-IOV。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3410
msgid "Check the deployed resources crd and pods:"
msgstr "检查已部署的资源 CRD 和 Pod："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3411
msgid "Check the label in the nodes."
msgstr "检查节点中的标签。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3412
msgid ""
"With all resources running, the label appears automatically in your node:"
msgstr "所有资源都运行后，标签会自动出现在您的节点中："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3413
msgid ""
"Review the <literal>daemonset</literal> to see the new <literal>sriov-"
"network-config-daemon</literal> and <literal>sriov-rancher-nfd-worker</"
"literal> as active and ready:"
msgstr ""
"查看 <literal>daemonset</literal>，您会看到新的 <literal>sriov-network-"
"config-daemon</literal> 和 <literal>sriov-rancher-nfd-worker</literal> "
"处于活动状态并已准备就绪："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3414
msgid ""
"In a few minutes (can take up to 10 min to be updated), the nodes are "
"detected and configured with the <literal>SR-IOV</literal> capabilities:"
msgstr "几分钟后（最多可能需要 10 分钟才会更新），将检测到节点，其上已配置了 <literal"
">SR-IOV</literal> 功能："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3415
msgid "Check the interfaces detected."
msgstr "检查已检测到的接口。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3416
msgid ""
"The interfaces discovered should be the PCI address of the network device. "
"Check this information with the <literal>lspci</literal> command in the host."
msgstr "发现的接口应为网络设备的 PCI 地址。请在主机中使用 <literal>lspci</literal> "
"命令检查此信息。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3417
msgid ""
"If your interface is not detected here, ensure that it is present in the "
"next config map:"
msgstr "如果此处未检测到您的接口，请确保该接口存在于下一个配置映射中："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3418
msgid ""
"If your device is not there, edit the config map, adding the right values to "
"be discovered (should be necessary to restart the <literal>sriov-network-"
"config-daemon</literal> daemonset)."
msgstr ""
"如果此处未检测到您的设备，请编辑配置映射，添加要发现的正确值（如有必要，"
"请重启 <literal>sriov-network-config-daemon</literal> daemonset）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3419
msgid ""
"Create the <literal>NetworkNode Policy</literal> to configure the "
"<literal>VFs</literal>."
msgstr "创建 <literal>NetworkNode 策略</literal>来配置 <literal>VF</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3420
msgid ""
"Some <literal>VFs</literal> (<literal>numVfs</literal>) from the device "
"(<literal>rootDevices</literal>) will be created, and it will be configured "
"with the driver <literal>deviceType</literal> and the <literal>MTU</literal>:"
msgstr ""
"将在设备 (<literal>rootDevices</literal>) 中创建一些 <literal>VF</literal> "
"(<literal>numVfs</literal>)，并在其上配置驱动程序 <literal>deviceType</"
"literal> 和 <literal>MTU</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3421
msgid ""
"The <literal>resourceName</literal> field must not contain any special "
"characters and must be unique across the cluster.  The example uses the "
"<literal>deviceType: vfio-pci</literal> because <literal>dpdk</literal> will "
"be used in combination with <literal>sr-iov</literal>. If you don’t use "
"<literal>dpdk</literal>, the deviceType should be <literal>deviceType: "
"netdevice</literal> (default value)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>resourceName</literal> "
"字段不得包含任何特殊字符，并且在整个群集中必须是唯一的。该示例使用 "
"<literal>deviceType: vfio-pci</literal>，因为 <literal>dpdk</literal> 将与 "
"<literal>sr-iov</literal> 结合使用。如果您不使用 <literal>dpdk</literal>，则 "
"deviceType 应为 <literal>deviceType: netdevice</literal>（默认值）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3422
msgid "Validate configurations:"
msgstr "验证配置："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3423
msgid ""
"Create the sr-iov network (optional, just in case a different network is "
"needed):"
msgstr "创建 sr-iov 网络（可选操作，仅在需要不同的网络时才执行）："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3424
msgid "Check the network created:"
msgstr "检查创建的网络："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3425
msgid "DPDK"
msgstr "DPDK"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3426
msgid ""
"<literal>DPDK</literal> (Data Plane Development Kit) is a set of libraries "
"and drivers for fast packet processing. It is used to accelerate packet "
"processing workloads running on a wide variety of CPU architectures.  The "
"DPDK includes data plane libraries and optimized network interface "
"controller (<literal>NIC</literal>) drivers for the following:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>DPDK</literal>（数据平面开发包）是一组用于实现快速数据包处理的库和驱"
"动程序。它用于加速各种 CPU 体系结构上运行的数据包处理工作负载。DPDK "
"包含以下组件的数据平面库和优化的网络接口控制器 (<literal>NIC</literal>) "
"驱动程序："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3427
msgid "A queue manager implements lockless queues."
msgstr "队列管理器，实现无锁队列。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3428
msgid "A buffer manager pre-allocates fixed size buffers."
msgstr "缓冲区管理器，预先分配固定大小的缓冲区。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3429
msgid ""
"A memory manager allocates pools of objects in memory and uses a ring to "
"store free objects; ensures that objects are spread equally on all "
"<literal>DRAM</literal> channels."
msgstr "内存管理器，在内存中分配对象池，并使用环来存储空闲对象；"
"确保对象均匀分布在所有 <literal>DRAM</literal> 通道上。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3430
msgid ""
"Poll mode drivers (<literal>PMD</literal>) are designed to work without "
"asynchronous notifications, reducing overhead."
msgstr "轮询模式驱动程序 "
"(<literal>PMD</literal>)，可在没有异步通知的情况下运行，从而降低开销。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3431
msgid ""
"A packet framework as a set of libraries that are helpers to develop packet "
"processing."
msgstr "作为一组库提供的数据包框架，可帮助开发数据包处理解决方案。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3432
msgid ""
"The following steps will show how to enable <literal>DPDK</literal> and how "
"to create <literal>VFs</literal> from the <literal>NICs</literal> to be used "
"by the <literal>DPDK</literal> interfaces:"
msgstr ""
"以下步骤说明如何启用 <literal>DPDK</literal>，以及如何从 <literal>NIC</"
"literal> 创建供 <literal>DPDK</literal> 接口使用的 <literal>VF</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3433
msgid "Install the <literal>DPDK</literal> package:"
msgstr "安装 <literal>DPDK</literal> 软件包："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3434
msgid "Kernel parameters:"
msgstr "内核参数："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3435
msgid ""
"To use DPDK, employ some drivers to enable certain parameters in the kernel:"
msgstr "要使用 DPDK，请采用一些驱动程序来启用内核中的某些参数："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3439 l10n/source/edge.xml:3460
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3887
msgid "iommu"
msgstr "iommu"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3440 l10n/source/edge.xml:3461
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3888
msgid "pt"
msgstr "pt"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3441
msgid ""
"This option enables the use of the <literal>vfio</literal> driver for the "
"DPDK interfaces."
msgstr "此选项允许为 DPDK 接口使用 <literal>vfio</literal> 驱动程序。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3442 l10n/source/edge.xml:3463
msgid "intel_iommu or amd_iommu"
msgstr "intel_iommu 或 amd_iommu"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3444
msgid ""
"This option enables the use of <literal>vfio</literal> for <literal>VFs</"
"literal>."
msgstr "此选项允许为 <literal>VF</literal> 使用 <literal>vfio</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3445
msgid ""
"To enable the parameters, add them to the <literal>/etc/default/grub</"
"literal> file:"
msgstr "要启用这些参数，请将其添加到 <literal>/etc/default/grub</literal> 文件中："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3446 l10n/source/edge.xml:3467
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3495
