#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3810
msgid ""
"As you can see, the example shows the configuration to enable the interface "
"with static IPs, as well as the configuration to enable the VLAN using the "
"base interface, once the following variables are replaced with the actual "
"values, according to your infrastructure:"
