"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-builder/blob/release-1.2/"
"docs/building-images.md#custom\">https://github.com/suse-edge/edge-image-"
"builder/blob/release-1.2/docs/building-images.md#custom</link>]) that looks "
"like:"
